---

<section
    class="section-rpg-roots relative py-32 md:py-60 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-visible bg-transparent"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div
            class="absolute -top-[15%] left-[-5%] w-[70%] h-[70%] bg-[#F24E29]/10 blur-[150px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen opacity-40"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute top-[20%] right-[10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-[#FFE8B2]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full opacity-30"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute -bottom-[20%] right-[-10%] w-[80%] h-[80%] bg-[#593622]/20 blur-[160px] rounded-full mix-blend-multiply"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0D0D0D] via-transparent to-[#0D0D0D] opacity-90"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto relative z-20 flex flex-col items-center gap-20"
    >
        <div
            class="w-full max-w-5xl relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-16 bg-[#F24E29]/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-60 transition-all duration-1000"
            >
            </div>

            <div
                class="relative bg-[#0D0D0D] p-2 border border-[#593622]/30 shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-12 h-12 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#F2B279]/40 z-30"
                >
                </div>

                <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[16/8]">
                    <img
                        src="/GreedFall/GreedFall_TheDyingWorld_Screenshot07.png"
                        alt="Inspiración RPG Clásico"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-[2500ms] group-hover:scale-110 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 shadow-[inset_0_0_120px_rgba(41,25,16,0.9)] pointer-events-none"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-10 relative translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#F2B279]"></div>
                <span
                    class="font-cinzel text-xs tracking-[0.4em] text-[#F2B279] uppercase"
                    >Tradición del Rol</span
                >
                <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#F2B279]"></div>
            </div>

            <h2
                class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-cinzel font-bold leading-[0.85] text-[#F2E6D8]"
            >
                Regreso a las <br />
                <span
                    class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F2B279] via-[#F24E29] to-[#593622]"
                >
                    Raíces
                </span>
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <p
                    class="text-[#F2E6D8]/80 text-xl lg:text-2xl font-serif italic leading-relaxed"
                >
                    GreedFall: The Dying World se inspira en títulos de culto
                    como <span class="text-[#F2B279] not-italic font-cinzel"
                        >Dragon Age: Inquisition</span
                    > y la saga <span
                        class="text-[#F2B279] not-italic font-cinzel"
                        >Baldur’s Gate</span
                    >.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-[#F2E6D8]/60 text-lg lg:text-xl font-serif leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Todos los ingredientes para seducir tanto a los fans como a
                    los jugadores en busca de una historia potente en un
                    universo original.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-6">
                <div
                    class="h-px w-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#593622] to-transparent"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-rpg-roots {
        contain: paint;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(
            to bottom,
            transparent,
            black 15%,
            black 85%,
            transparent
        );
    }
</style>
